PS:
btw, looks like coq is not really fond of this data type:

Inductive t a : Type :=
  | E : t a
  | D : t a -> t a -> t a
  | O : a -> t a
  | I : t (t a) -> t a
.

Error: Non strictly positive occurrence of "t" in "t (t a) -> t a".

